SelecciÃ³n basada en la relaciÃ³n

WITH rio_genil AS (
    SELECT ST_Union(geom) AS geom
    FROM red_hidrografica
    WHERE nombre = 'RÃ­o Genil'
)
SELECT 
    m.*
FROM 
    municipios m
JOIN 
    rio_genil r
ON 
    ST_Intersects(m.geom, r.geom);

SelecciÃ³n basada en la relaciÃ³n (y ii)

WITH rio_genil_grupo AS (
  WITH rio_genil AS (
    SELECT grupo
    FROM red_hidrografica
    WHERE nombre = 'RÃ­o Genil'
    GROUP BY grupo
  )
  SELECT 
    1 AS id,
    'RÃ­o Genil' as nombre, 
    ST_Union(geom) AS geom
  FROM red_hidrografica
  WHERE grupo = 
    (SELECT grupo FROM rio_genil)
  GROUP BY grupo
)
SELECT 
  m.*
FROM 
  municipios m
JOIN 
  rio_genil_grupo r
ON 
  ST_Intersects(m.geom, r.geom);

IntersecciÃ³n (y ii)

WITH provincia AS (
  SELECT ST_Union(geom) AS geom
  FROM municipios
)
SELECT 
  dh.nombre,
  ST_Intersection(dh.geom, pr.geom) AS geom,
  ST_Area(ST_Intersection(dh.geom, pr.geom)) / 
  ST_Area(pr.geom) * 100 AS tpc_dh
FROM
  distritos_hidrograficos dh,
  provincia pr
WHERE 
  ST_Intersects(dh.geom, pr.geom);

  JOIN

  ON

  WHERE 
        m.municipio = 'LanjarÃ³n'
